title: Soy Products
description: A soy products store situated on the Central market(Piatsa Centrala), row 25 on the right side, and near Armeneasca street. Sells fresh tofu, tofu pate with 4 different flavours with no preservatives, soy sausages, grilled tofu, soy cutlets, soymilk based crepes with potato, jam and tofu stuffings, vegan mayonnaise, and soy sauce.
